{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"NodeList.item","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/item","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/entries\"><code>entries()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/forEach\"><code>forEach()</code></a></li><li><em><code>item()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/keys\"><code>keys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/values\"><code>values()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>根据给定的索引，返回一个 <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-536297177\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>NodeList</code></a>对象中包含的 Node 对象。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>nodeItem</em> = <em>nodeList</em>.item(<em>index</em>)\n</pre>\n<ul>\n <li><code>nodeList</code>是一个<code>NodeList</code>对象。通常是由某个 DOM 属性或方法返回的，比如<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\" title=\"zh-cn/DOM/Node.childNodes\">childNodes</a>.</li>\n <li><code>index</code> 是给定的索引。从 0 开始。</li>\n <li><code>nodeItem</code> 是根据索引<code>index</code> 由 <code>item</code> 方法从 <code>nodeList</code> 中获取到的节点。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>JavaScript 有更简单的语法来从一个 NodeList 对象中获取指定索引的节点：</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>nodeItem</em> = <em>nodeList</em>[<em>index</em>]\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例子","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">var tables = document.getElementsByTagName(\"table\");\nvar firstTable = tables.item(1); // 或者简写为 tables[1]，返回一个文档中的第二个 table 元素。\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"备注","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果索引越界，该方法不会抛出异常，只会返回 <code>null</code>。</p>\n<p><code>item()</code> 不是 DOM <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/element\" title=\"zh-cn/DOM/element\">元素</a>或者 DOM 节点的方法，而是 NodeList 对象的方法。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#method-item\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: NodeList.item()</a></p>\n<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-844377136\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: NodeList.item()</a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"根据给定的索引，返回一个 NodeList对象中包含的 Node 对象。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"NodeList.item()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"NodeList.item()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"NodeList.item","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"NodeList.item()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/nodelist/item","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/nodelist/item/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList","title":"NodeList"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList/item","title":"NodeList.item"}],"pageTitle":"NodeList.item - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}